Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该声明中称Celestial Being拥有机动兵器Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们宇宙军录下的未确认的MS影像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方最新锐的机体一下子就被…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:51.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是想牵制新兵器开发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多于条约规定的军队驻扎在轨道电梯中的事被公开了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各方面都要求公开信息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也有报告称这是人革联或是联合的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能极秘密地开发最先进MS的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.23,0:05:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要发达国家水平的技术和预算
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是  武装组织应该有强有力的后盾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但各国的间谍机构并未获得与组织有关的可靠情报
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够确定的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.83,0:05:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自称Celestial Being的武装组织
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:36.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保有凌驾于我方的Enact的MS这一事实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用武力来根除战争啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:51.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪比特  他们好像能代替我国
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总统  他们是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:56.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不求任何回报
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要介入他国的纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了确保国民的安全和国家利益
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不是什么慈善事业
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该很快就能揭下面具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的使命是到时候对他们进行制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轨道电梯运行已有10年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在经济开始稳定的时候却发生了这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是哪个国家的新闻都在谈论我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:37.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「神秘武装集团」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「向全世界宣称要根除战争」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.41,0:06:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  大部分人似乎都并不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然那样  就要让他们相信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为已经说过「Celestial Being的理念仅在于行动」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王留美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:57.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到第二个任务了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.58,0:07:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用回部队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  闹得这么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想知道Gundam的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台机体太特殊了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.55,0:07:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗能力不用多言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个一出现
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会导致雷达  通信  电子装置发生故障
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是因为那光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片桐  那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前只能说是种特殊粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计那光芒是由光子的分裂现象形成的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特殊粒子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是粒子  我认为那台机体还有其它秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怀有好意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指的是相当感兴趣的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:07:58.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉哈姆·艾卡中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比利·片桐技术顾问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是返回MSWAD的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于3300开始第二任务
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一边  于3300…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,测试机体的实战吗  真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是为了今后  也有必要摸清Gundam的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.05,0:08:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  硬要你这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在有觉悟的基础上参加的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很强嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不想成为弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是年轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普特利麦奥斯  箱体于固定位置静止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios  请以C装备前去弹射器甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密转为弹射模式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按预定时间  按预定计划进行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.63,0:09:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN系统休眠解除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:28.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操作权  转给刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.43,0:09:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  出击吧  搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios已在线性区域固定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射时刻转由Kyrios掌控
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认控制  Kyrios
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亚·哈普提兹姆  进入介入行动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舱门打开  舱门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  Dynames  准备出击  准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue已进入弹射器甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于线性区域固定  发射准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射时刻转由Virtue掌控
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue  提耶利亚·埃德  出击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子  开始散布  开始散布
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:02.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执行第二任务
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂·斯托拉托斯  出击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  那才是体现Celestial Being理念的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子  最大范围散布
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向机体前方展开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:37.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模拟训练虽然做过好几次…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:39.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵达下降点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始突入大气层
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  该说他胆子大呢还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉  E传感器有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有物体突入大气层
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:12:00.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  我可没收到这种报告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示最大远程影像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说那机体能单独突入大气层吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体的进攻路线呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.37,0:12:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若照目前的状态  预计下降点是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,印度南部  锡兰岛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.75,0:12:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在我们的领土内  中校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:29.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们真的想要武力介入吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子从最大范围散布转为普通模式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:46.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是Kyrios
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务现在才开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了哦  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿里路亚和提耶利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.93,0:12:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已确认
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:13:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在预定地点汇合后  进入第一阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是去印度南部的原斯里兰卡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锡兰岛？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,356)\fs22}Ceylon
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人革联展开的那个地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按预定采取措施
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那样好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定能把那机体弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锡兰岛现处于无政府状态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是多数派的僧伽罗人和少数派的泰米尔人的民族纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战争从20世纪起断断续续地持续着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being将以武力介入这场民族纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民族纷争…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.65,0:13:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是原斯里兰卡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:14:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得人革联在10年前支持的是少数派的泰米尔人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.35,0:14:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  虽然以和平解决纷争为名  但其实不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人革联的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.34,0:14:16.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了确保穿越锡兰岛东部海底的太阳能的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那周围泰米尔人的势力较强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  纷争因人革联的介入而进一步恶化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以致陷入了无政府状态
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.82,0:14:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟机长说一声  改变进路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并拜托一下Flag的整备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧  那样太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.84,0:15:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消灭了敌方部队的30%
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,0:15:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样一举歼灭他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉  本部有紧急联络
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being好像过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  要来这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向各部队传达
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各自按皇·李·诺瑞加的战况预测采取措施
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期望有那样的战果  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要彻彻底底地干一番
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你便
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  在听吗  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:15:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  回话啊  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:36.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦保护小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入作战行动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂…  你们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.32,0:16:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下下签  下下签
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:46.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中进行炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回避运动就交给你了  哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.11,0:17:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.63,0:17:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  确认纷争  进行根除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.42,0:17:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没有损伤！？  这是什么装甲…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames  对目标进行狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全灭  全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气势太过头了  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios  爆击目标
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此还真成了稀世的杀人者…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.43,0:18:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.39,0:18:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然变形了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.16,0:18:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:18:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉目标  转入歼灭行动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退  撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢配合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.74,0:19:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人溃败了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该偿还之前欠的债了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  找到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答对了  绢江
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.59,0:20:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥里亚·修亨贝格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  此人在200年前就已死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being出现了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武力干涉原斯里兰卡的内部纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.57,0:20:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向双方展开了攻击！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.81,0:20:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向双方展开了攻击？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做明明只会使双方的感情进一步恶化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being  到底在想些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的以为靠一次军事介入就能结束持续了300多年的纷争吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只一次  会一直介入的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.25,0:21:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至纷争结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至憎恨指向我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是伴随改变事物的疼痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会被干掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,0:21:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是首次介入纷争  他有自己的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他会是Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合的运输机？  在这个空域？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Flag吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.56,0:21:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:21:59.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉哈姆·艾卡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你的存在夺走了内心的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.24,0:23:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能接受连对话都要拒绝的行为吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.24,0:23:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对摆在眼前的刀刃  少年感受到了时代的变革
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.67,0:23:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「变化的世界」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.95,0:23:47.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是无法指定的现实
